channel.title: I got 2 problems I need help with
channel.description:
1. My server wont load...here is wat it says
Starting HippieScape V2 on 0.0.0.0:43594 Commands LOADED Objects LOADED ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:1279 Client type: low memory version UserId: 3912391 Brod is signing onto the server Game saved for player Brod ClientHandler: Client Brod disconnected
I tried really hard to get it all right, I hope I did
2. I cant get my server online I have 2 computers. I have a no-ip. But I think its my Port Forwarding skills. They suck. I cant get on with the other computer and I keep trying. But it never works. When it says what port to forward do I enter 43594? Oh and My computer wont let me into my firewall settings...I think its God of Ikiliki's guide that tells me I gotta change em but on Tico's guide it doesnt say...Im kinda confused
